    "name": "耶兰多的低语：克苏鲁选集",
    "steam_appid": 3255870,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《耶兰多的低语：克苏鲁选集》中，你将置身于一个被克苏鲁阴霾笼罩的世界，感受克拉夫特式的绝望宿命感。游戏采用纯粹的碎片化叙事风格，以风云变幻的兹维达城为背景，沙皇俄国的余晖与布尔什维克革命的浪潮激烈碰撞，政治动荡不安，每一处角落都暗藏着未知的危险与秘密，时刻挑战着理智的极限。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255870/extras/1233d56fd42a943bfaf72b42a2c0e326.avif?t=1772096105\" width=616 height=78 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将通过掷骰这一充满随机性的机制来获取线索碎片，在混沌无序的世界中摸索，试图抓住那一丝真相的曙光。从含混不清的呓语, 古老建筑的隐秘符号中，收集数百条线索。这些线索看似零散且毫无关联，如同梦境与幻象，但每一条都可能是解开谜题的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255870/extras/fb44937fa6ab7d9c24c9a3577c52e9da.poster.avif?t=1772096105\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255870/extras/fb44937fa6ab7d9c24c9a3577c52e9da.webm?t=1772096105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255870/extras/fb44937fa6ab7d9c24c9a3577c52e9da.mp4?t=1772096105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255870/extras/bcc69d5226e9a5da4deda2d0330bf7b1.avif?t=1772096105\" width=616 height=78 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏基于TOC的核心理念，面对收集到的线索碎片，将它们拼接整合才是重点。随着《耶兰多》背后的秘密逐渐浮出水面，仿佛在黑暗中慢慢看清了那不可名状之物的轮廓...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255870/extras/44cb83270f2d8e6fd00a3947cbe91eb1.poster.avif?t=1772096105\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255870/extras/44cb83270f2d8e6fd00a3947cbe91eb1.webm?t=1772096105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255870/extras/44cb83270f2d8e6fd00a3947cbe91eb1.mp4?t=1772096105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255870/extras/598097f6b01c44c2248aa3f0704061c9.avif?t=1772096105\" width=616 height=78 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的分层纸雕风格呈现了梦幻与惊悚交织的独特美学。每一处建筑都像是精心雕琢的艺术品。在这如梦如幻的场景背后，却隐藏着解开谜题的重要线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255870/extras/a2fd1f8884905ca05af3c0560ebdf87f.poster.avif?t=1772096105\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255870/extras/a2fd1f8884905ca05af3c0560ebdf87f.webm?t=1772096105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255870/extras/a2fd1f8884905ca05af3c0560ebdf87f.mp4?t=1772096105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
